<tr class="bg0"><td>&nbsp;</td><td><a name='int_15cc4a1' href='http://dbtropes.org/resource/Film/ThePatriot/int_15cc4a1'>Film: The Patriot / int_15cc4a1</a></td>
<td><div title='http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type'>type</div></td>
