<td><i>Cheese-Eating Surrender Monkeys: Quite well averted. Maj. Villeneuve is a stalwart ally to the Colonials and an all-around Bad Ass, and the French army shows up at the end to play The Cavalry force the British to surrender.</i></td>
</tr>


