<tr class="bg1"><td>&nbsp;</td><td><a name='int_c37c98bb' href='http://dbtropes.org/resource/Film/ThePatriot/int_c37c98bb'>Film: The Patriot / int_c37c98bb</a></td>
<td><div title='http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type'>type</div></td>
<td><a href='http://dbtropes.org/resource/Main/HistoricalVillainUpgrade'>Historical Villain Upgrade</a></td>
